                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380618-name-1191" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-1191" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-1191" type="surname" value="COPPIN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-1191" type="given" value="EDWARD GEORGE"></interp>EDWARD GEORGE COPPIN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a gentleman's servant. I was at Greenwich fair on the 6th of June just before nine o'clock; I had a hand<lb></lb>kerchief in my pocket—I was told I was robbed in about five minutes—I saw the prisoner behind me, and caught hold of his arm, when the police<lb></lb>man asked roe to render him assistance.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380618-name-1192" type="witnessName">
