                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-1192" type="surname" value="BROOK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-1192" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES BROOK</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable L.</hi> 118.) I was on duty, and watched the prisoner between three and four minutes—he was in company with another—I saw the prisoner take a handkerchief from the prosecutor's pocket—I laid hold of him and the other—the handkerchief was lost. <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never saw it—when I put my band towards the young man next to me I was only showing him what was going on—I did not know him.</p>
